      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GAMBELLA (7) impressive display when ran right away after running them ragged to make it two in a row, scoring at this track over 515m (29.05). Winner at her latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Expected to be right there at the finish again. POINT BREAK (8) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and three placings from nine starts. Below best last time at The Meadows (30.50) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 6 length fourth. Looks suited here and can measure up. TALCOTT BALE (2) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 1 last run (29.57) at this track. Boasts a strong record from this draw with five wins and five minor placings from 11 starts. Likely to be in the finish again. FOXY ROXY (1) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
